learning_outcomes.en:
The student 
- knows the history of education of students with blindness and low-vision
- knows the main causes of visual impairment;
- knows the special needs and the developmental differences in children with BVI. 
- knows the special methods of teaching children with visual impairment;
- is familiar with rehabilitation possibilities and special devices;
- knows the terminology of the field.

learning_outcomes.et:
Üliõpilane:
- tunneb tüflopedagoogika ajalugu;
- teab nägemispuude peamisi põhjusi;
- on kursis pimedate ja vaegnägijate õpetamise erimetoodikaga, rehabiliteerimise võimalustega ning abivahenditega;
- valdab erialast terminoloogiat.
